						 <p>There is nothing I don't like about this. I actually had to stop reading it last night and finish it today, it was that unsettling. It hits the perfect note of almost-reality and wrongness that makes up the best stuff on this site.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
