					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My one criticism would be that there seems to be no thread. Or, rather, that I can't find one and don't know if one is intended; it's perfectly okay if these have no relationship to each other whatsoever. I like that you avoided the standard &quot;viewing it makes stuff happen&quot; trope.</p> <p>One other thing. The image is captioned as -11, but what's there looks like what I'd imagine -12 to be. Not sure if that was an oversight or not.</p> 
				 	]]>
